children.subject: Hi, when we're asked in to fill out our courses, do we just fill in 7 units of electives, or all the CS/EE courses we plan to take? CS182 isn't showing up, and I wanted to take that as my design course. Thanks!

This is a friendly reminder to complete your CS Major declaration application if you are ready to declare the major. The CS Major Summer Application Deadline is Friday 8/30/19 at 11:59 p.m.

 

You can find the application by visiting -  https://eecs.berkeley.edu/academics/undergraduate/cs-ba
